title: TonightsGirlfriend - Nicole Aniston NEW 02 July 2016
description:
I'm a personal trainer, so naturally I'm into really fit girls. Nicole Aniston is one of the fittest girls I've seen in the business so I have known for a while that I had to meet her. I finally get her over to my room and we do a little role playing. We stick with the fit theme and have Nicole role play that she's a girl I picked up at the gym and has stopped by my house to fit in an extra naughty workout.
